<HEAD>First National Bank Of Omaha Reaches Agreement To Buy Columbus
Bank</HEAD>
<DATELINE>OMAHA, Neb. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   First National of Omaha Inc. has reached an
agreement to buy the holding company of First National Bank of
Columbus, a transaction Omaha bank officials described as the
largest bank acquisition in the state's history.
   If federal regulators approve the deal, First National, holding
company of the First National Bank of Omaha, would pay about $22
